Enum TransactionType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TransactionType>
      • com.abc.TransactionType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TransactionType>

    public enum TransactionType
extends java.lang.Enum<TransactionType>
    An enumeration of all the possible transaction types. It creates type safety for creating transactions within the banking application.

    We also use an OpCode to determine what effect a transaction will have on an account balance.

    Author:
    Jeff
